description	"Archetype: HK-Series Assassin Droid

Class: Mandalorian.
Class Summary: 
Heavily armored sniper and assassin equipt to terminate force wielders. 

Weaponry:
- Heavy Melee
- Droid Assassin's Rifle (Based on EE-3 level 3)
- Frag Grenades (2)
- Sonic Detonator (1)
- Trip Mine (1)

Holdables:
- Cloaking Device
- Portable Sentry Gun

Attributes:
- Fuel (2)
- Regenerating Shields (1)
- Immune to Mind Trick
- Invisible to Force Sense
- Magnetic Plating
- Blast Armor
- Cortosis Armor

Abilties:
- Poison Darts (2) [Alt Ability 3 while in melee]
- Wrist Flamethrower [Class Special 2]
- Wrist Laser [Class Special 2]

~HK-47: A Hunter-Killer assassin droid and Jedi hunter constructed by the Dark Lord of the Sith Darth Revan to assassinate targets whom he had deemed threats to galactic stability and peace.
----------
~HK-50 and HK-51: After finding a hidden HK manufacturing plant on Telos IV, HK-47 reprogrammed the newer models found within to suit his own purposes."